reviewText: This was a gift to my Daughter. This is her favorite series. I would recommend to go with the separate packaging, instead of the full package deal. This way is a lot cheaper. If there is one that doesn't work you just send that one in.
Loved getting 2 seasons in one....not bulky at all.  Love re-watching the Friends seasons, they keep me laughing even now!
Fast delivery,  great quality. Fast delivery,  great quality. Love it! It came quickly and the DVD's have so many features besides the shows. Nice to see behind the scenes.

Best season yet as it is the final. New additions will be added to complete the show and relationships we have seen through the years will grow. Nice way to see this show close as we now know what's in store for our friends.

To this day my wife and I quote lines from Friends. Even though its been off the air for over ten years there is always something comforting about turning on an episode of Friends. You ever feeling kinda blue? Then pop in a season of Friends and you'll cheer up in minutes.

This completed the series for my collection.  In my humble opinion "Friends" is one of the top ten television comedy series ever.  For anyone who has ever been part of a group of tight knit friends....this series is a well written, well acted reminder of the ups and downs, ins and outs, triumphs and tragedies, pain and pleasure of that dynamic.  It is a series that stands the test of time and will entertain you and fill your heart over and over as you continue to enjoy its life like quirkiness.
My 17 year old has begged for entire season.  Didn't buy all at 1 time and still a great price on Amazon!  Recommend to anyone!

Sorry to see it end, but they did tie up their young people into adulthood pretty nicely.  I so wish they would have done some movies along the way to show how the gang continued on....hopefully happily ever afters with Ross and Rachel, Monica and Chandler and family, Phoebe and Mike.  At least we did get another year and a half of Joey....still not enough.  I don't think I could ever get enough of these characters.  Very enjoyable from writing to main characters, to friends of friends, love them all.
Great value for the price. Two full seasons in a compact case.  This is exactly what I was looking for and I paid much less than expected

I liked this series while it was airing on network television and have enjoyed the repeats on several television channels, but some of the highlights of owning these DVDs is to be able to see the entire episode. Often the repeats do not have the entire show, to afford more commercials to air.
But if you enjoyed the series, you'll love the bonus features, especially the gag reels, usually on the final DVD of the season, along with several fun games.
